(244, 'Disabled Product Status for Search Engines', 'DISABLED_PRODUCTS_TRIGGER_HTTP200', 'false', 'When a product is marked Disabled (status=0) but is not deleted from the database, should Search Engines still show it as Available?<br>eg:<br>True = Return HTTP 200 response<br>False = Return HTTP 410<br>(Deleting it will return HTTP 404)<br><b>Default: false</b>', 9, 10, NULL, '2023-05-18 19:11:00', NULL, 'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),', NULL),
