(447, 'Category Header Menu ON/OFF', 'CATEGORIES_TABS_STATUS', '1', 'Category Header Nav<br />This enables the display of your store\'s categories as a menu across the top of your header. There are many potential creative uses for this.<br />0= Hide Categories Tabs<br />1= Show Categories Tabs', 19, 112, NULL, '2023-05-18 19:11:05', NULL, 'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'0\', \'1\'), ', NULL),
